Next.js Rules:

1. Use App Router only.
2. Use Server Components by default.
3. Add "use client" only when needed.
4. Prefer Server Actions when appropriate.
5. Use loading.tsx.
6. Use error.tsx.
7. Use route groups.
8. Use metadata API for SEO.
9. Use dynamic imports for heavy components.
10. Optimize images using next/image.
11. Never use pages router.
12. Use Suspense when appropriate.
